SELECT i.initiative_id, i.initiative_name, o.org_name FROM initiatives AS i JOIN organizations AS o ON i.org_id = o.org_id WHERE i.initiative_date > '2021-01-01';
SELECT o.org_id, o.org_name, COUNT(i.initiative_id) AS total_initiatives FROM organizations AS o LEFT JOIN initiatives AS i ON o.org_id = i.org_id GROUP BY o.org_id, o.org_name;
SELECT org_name, COUNT(initiative_id) AS total_initiatives FROM organizations AS o LEFT JOIN initiatives AS i ON o.org_id = i.org_id GROUP BY org_name ORDER BY total_initiatives DESC;
